{"tid":993710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1天啪28次！60歲巨乳富婆「用完即丟」甩第14任鮮肉夫","createTime":"2019-01-24T06:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T07:06:11.000Z","uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"67ec1e59d15fe69cf7434052ed38d85d85b92c20","tid":993710,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T06:33:47.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n泰國女知名企業家莉娜（Leena Jungjanya）曾在電視公開徵婚，要求對方要有能力「每天床戰28次」引起轟動。現年60歲的她，有消息傳出她又換掉第14任老公，正在尋覓下一個鮮肉。<br />\n▼ 莉娜蒂第14任小鮮肉老公。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3857/d3857099.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3857%2Fd3857099.jpg&h=1e36fea2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據中國《騰訊網》報導，莉娜在泰國早已是一名網紅，本業是一名律師，目前經營化妝品企業「High Society」的她，經常上節目亮相，而她的情史比事業成就還備受大家關注，曾於2017年在電視公開徵婚，要求第9任老公必須要「有6塊肌、年約25歲、身高180公分、體重70公斤以下」，而且最重要的是要能「每天床戰28次」。當時消息一出後，儘管條件嚴苛仍吸引超過5萬人報名參加，並由25歲小鮮肉蘭希（Rangsee）脫穎而出。只是同年數星期之後，莉娜已換了好幾任老公，改由25歲號稱有「20公分巨雕」的陽光型男多姆（Dom）當自己的第12任老公。<br />\n據了解，莉娜在2年內，已經換到第14任，平均4個月就要換一名老公，「啪完就丟」的行徑讓人大開眼界。儘管莉娜今年已60歲，但她的感情世界仍引起許多大眾注意，緋聞也一直沒有停止過。日前網路上流傳一組莉娜的辣照，短短數小時內即吸引100多萬觀看次數，也引發網友熱議。<br />\n▼ 莉娜曾在2017年曾帶第9任老公蘭希上電視節目。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3857/d3857080.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3857%2Fd3857080.jpg&h=1602f1ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼ 莉娜在同年數星期之後，火速甩掉數任老公，並帶著號稱有「20公分巨雕」的第12任新歡多姆亮相。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3857/d3857081.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3857%2Fd3857081.jpg&h=daa8f154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最近又有新消息指出，有網友表示，莉娜早已和第14任老公離婚，與另一位男性展開新戀情。她日前也證實已經把第14任給「休」了，但她離婚後不為情傷所苦，為了保持妖嬈姿態，先前還特地「進廠維修」，更不避諱曬出整形後，腫成豬頭的照片，近日也貼出術後復原的巨乳美照，不過從近期流傳的照片中來看，許多網友懷疑她只是修圖修很大。<br />\n▼ 整型後的莉娜有濃眉大眼，還有相當火辣的深V身材。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3857/d3857082.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3857%2Fd3857082.jpg&h=5427f6b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼ 麗娜先前曾PO出自己整型時的照片。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3857/d3857084.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3857%2Fd3857084.jpg&h=9248ff30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190124/1364289.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190124%2F1364289.htm&d=%2Bga%2BB%2FGfR5Xrt1IO9jR1Lhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=a3795d78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190124/1364289.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e650d658cbc9c4de7a2b824e5d0b50c65e005e7f","tid":993710,"uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T06:34:52.000Z","msg":"泰國離婚唔洗分身家？"},{"pid":"41add423bd6af47369f66435a7e2ec134364776b","tid":993710,"uid":134997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T06:38:22.000Z","msg":"好想佢用錢掉鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n塞d銀紙落我屎眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用美金磨我龜頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一路騎一路大叫<br />\n「臭鴨，今晚一q十皮」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n射左之後再用銀紙抹返乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c22d229a7c56d0dc811df20c242e02af28cbf8d","tid":993710,"uid":193642,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T06:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3857/d3857082.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3857%2Fd3857082.jpg&h=99b40dc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依張圖明明係key個樣上去個身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2730ff3b1e2e21d348b69bb990d3be75faf90d5","tid":993710,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T06:43:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>她日前也證實已經把第14任給「休」了，但她離婚後不為情傷所苦，為了保持<span style=\"color: red;\">妖嬈姿態</span>，先前還特地「進廠維修」，更不避諱曬出整形後，腫成豬頭的照片，近日也貼出術後復原的巨乳美照，不過從近期流傳的照片中來看，許多網友懷疑她只是修圖修很大。</blockquote><br />\n係咪唔知「妖嬈」點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a80eed53b7f4a955d879e63eb65c69b5f1c17d","tid":993710,"uid":71342,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T06:48:32.000Z","msg":"嘩～最尾張相打輸泰拳咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700f2453775fdbaf5b455b53fd3229cfe46cab47","tid":993710,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T07:06:11.000Z","msg":"有錢真好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}